se-bottom-row.png?resize=2048%2C298&amp;ssl=1 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 2640px) 100vw, 2640px" /></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class="wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained" id="community" style="padding-top:0;padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--edge-space);padding-bottom:5rem;padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--edge-space)">\n<div class="wp-block-group alignwide is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow">\n<div style="margin-top:40px;margin-bottom:40px;height:60px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer is-style-dots-background"></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class="wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-5 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex" style="padding-top:40px;padding-bottom:40px">\n<div class="wp-block-column has-charcoal-0-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-69164e22c9f712b2671f120dd34a4b9b is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow" style="flex-basis:50%">\n<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-heading-3-font-size" style="margin-top:0">Meet the WordPress community</h2>\n\n\n\n<p class="is-style-short-text">Behind the technology is a diverse collective of people collaborating and gathering from around the world. We hold regular events with opportunities to learn more about WordPress and the latest tech trends, connect with fellow industry experts, and foster your professional growth.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p class="is-style-short-text">We’re united by the spirit of open source, and the freedom to build, transform, and share without barriers. Everyone is welcome.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class="has-link-color wp-elements-4df4d77e5641a95aeffbd93f8cccdc8e" style="margin-top:30px"><a href="https://events.wordpress.org/">Find an event near you</a></p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow" style="flex-basis:50%">\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img width="1216" height="593" src="https://wordpress.org/files/2024/04/photo-community-1.png" alt="A black and white photograph of excited, applauding attendees in the audience at a WordPress event." class="wp-image-39810" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2024/04/photo-community-1.png?w=1216&amp;ssl=1 1216w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2024/04/photo-community-1.png?resize=300%2C146&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2024/04/photo-community-1.png?resize=1024%2C499&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2024/04/photo-community-1.png?resize=768%2C375&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1216px) 100vw, 1216px" /></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class="wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-6 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex" style="margin-top:5rem">\n<div class="wp-block-column has-charcoal-0-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-69164e22c9f712b2671f120dd34a4b9b is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow" style="flex-basis:50%">\n<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-inter-font-family" style="font-size:18px;line-height:1.88"><strong>Build for yourself, not by yourself</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p class="is-style-short-text">Whether you’re an entrepreneur, professional developer, or first-time blogger, there’s a library of resources and learning tools ready for you. Plus, you have the whole WordPress community in your corner.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class="wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-11 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained" style="margin-top:30px">\n<p class="has-link-color wp-elements-4df4d77e5641a95aeffbd93f8cccdc8e"><a href="https://learn.wordpress.org/" data-type="link" data-id="https://learn.wordpress.org/">Learn how to use WordPress</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class="has-link-color wp-elements-4df4d77e5641a95aeffbd93f8cccdc8e"><a href="https://wordpress.org/playground/" data-type="link" data-id="https://wordpress.org/playground/">Test WordPress out in your browser</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class="has-link-c